General.Name: Red Metal Ltd
General.Description: Red Metal Limited acquires and explores for mineral properties in Australia. It primarily explores for copper, gold, silver, lead, zinc, cobalt, and nickel deposits. It holds 100% interest in the Maronan, Gidyea, Corkwood, Pardoo, Nullarbor, Punt Hill and Pernatty Lagoon, Gulf, Sybella, Brunette Downs, and Birthday Well projects located in Australia. The company also holds interests in the Lawn Hill, Mount Skipper, Barton, Three Ways, Mallapunyah, Irindina, and Yarrie projects. Red Metal Limited was incorporated in 2003 and is based in Sydney, Australia.
